OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with showers, perhaps merging
OL,7,Fto longer spells of rain. Overnight,
OL,8,Fshowers clearing south of Shetland,
OL,9,Fbecoming confined to Orkney. Moderate
OL,10,For fresh northwesterly winds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FShowers clearing to the south
OL,13,Fof Orkney in the morning to leave a
OL,14,Fdry day with sunny spells for all
OL,15,Fareas. Light to moderate southeasterly
OL,16,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
